Subject:Re: [Koha] debarred a patrons account automatically the account
	expires
> How can I configure koha to debarred/Restricted a patrons account automatically when
> the patrons' account expires

Koha won't do this for you automatically, although it seems like it
would be a fairly simple enhancement. I think the important question
is: What can your expired patrons do that you don't want them to,
leading you to want to restrict them?

